{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9317040f24","title":"关于国际关系与国共关系的估计给周恩来的通报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"934c0471f1","index":0,"year":1941,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"9317040f24"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji15.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji15":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a643675fcc","type":"paragraph","text":"关于国际关系与国共关系的估计","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"9317040f24"},{"id":"fba510cc5d","type":"paragraph","text":"给周恩来的通报","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"9317040f24"},{"id":"a81bc6b3d8","type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年3月17日）（一）蒋急于转圆，似乎是由于近日国际关系（二）松冈西行目的在订立日德、日苏两种条约，两约如订大战即发，英美要阻止日苏订约、命蒋向中共转圈，落亦甚俱日苏亲善，似有求助于我之意，日本则利用国共恶化，有求苏助日制蒋意。（三）如日苏只订经济条约不订政治条约，则蒋有答应我临时办法各条可能，如日苏订立政治条约，则国共中苏关系均可能一时恶化。（四）（略）。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"9317040f24"}],"page":{"id":"dfc65083c1","publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"9317040f24","start":482,"end":482}}}},"__N_SSG":true}